  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to investigate the clinical effects of multiple (28 day)
      twice-daily doses of OC000459 in comparison to placebo on clinic lung function (FEV1) in mild
      to moderate asthmatics with an FEV1 of 60-80% of predicted and requiring only short acting
      inhaled B2-adrenergic agonists for symptomatic control.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
